1.project home:
	http://code.google.com/p/xgcom/

2.get source by svn:
	svn checkout http://xgcom.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ xgcom

3.get source in tar ball:
	http://code.google.com/p/xgcom/downloads/list

4.library needed while compiling:
	ubuntu: make, automake，libglib2.0-dev，libvte-dev，libgtk2.0-dev
	fedora or centos:  
		sudo yum install automake glib2-devel.x86_64 vte-devel gtk2-devel.x86_64
		sudo yum group install 'Development Tools'

5.compile steps:
 
	xgcom$ ./autogen.sh
	xgcom$ make
	xgcom$ sudo make install
	xgcom$ xgcom
